            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%B4%E5%8F%91%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A4%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%B4%E5%8F%91%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E6%B4%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%A4%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#头发这样洗一周只用洗一次头#</span></a>】洗头时，￼专家提醒这3点：①一般推荐每天洗一次或两天洗一次头发，不推荐一天内多次洗头发；②洗头发的水温建议控制在37℃-40℃之间；③洗发水建议先放在手心揉搓，不要直接倒在头皮上👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4968334182252572" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hjvqf59t2zj21hc0u0djh.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/r52CS5rplx08abNFyDzG01041200ah1j0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1700817312&amp;ssig=ZHkG0gv5j9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/yJflJy2olx08abNFbEgE0104120053qg0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1700817312&amp;ssig=Ybw%2F3fhMFu&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dcPbJx6Klx08abNEIr7O0104120039Pe0E010.m